job_name = "CHAR_THE_PILGRIM"
description = "Wu Song, the Pilgrim. In the legend he killed a man-eating tiger bare-handed, then took a darker revenge and walked it off as a wandering penitent. Here an underground combat-streamer who once beat a Static bare-handed on camera, then did a worse thing for love. With every cut he asks whether vengeance is justice or only more fuel. His archived reels are the only proof he was ever real."
